{"tid":2516101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"5歲女童虐殺案 繼母與繼外婆齊提上訴","createTime":"2021-05-04T12:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T14:45:44.000Z","uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc316b87c3523a7b972b7b7ca6ff6d5470ec21b","tid":2516101,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"5歲女童Z遭虐待致死一案，女童的親父及繼母早前被裁定謀殺罪成，繼母的母親亦被裁定忽略Z及X。法官黃崇厚就謀殺罪判處父母終身監禁，另兩人承認的殘暴對待兒童罪則判囚9年半，與謀殺罪刑期同期執行，而繼母母親則判監5年。律政司今回覆查詢指，<strong><span class=\"red\">繼母已就其謀殺罪定罪申請上訴許可，並就其殘暴對待兒童罪的刑期提出上訴</span></strong>；至於繼母母親亦就其定罪及刑罰申請上訴。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210504/ODYCVSHM5ZE7BN67354MUIGL7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210504%2FODYCVSHM5ZE7BN67354MUIGL7Q%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=2240b506\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210504%2FODYCVSHM5ZE7BN67354MUIGL7Q%2F&h=eea1fa44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210504/ODYCVSHM5ZE7BN67354MUIGL7Q/</a>"},{"pid":"4a4764068a0adef14208a1c77a68a2ea7f24fe07","tid":2516101,"uid":332417,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:18:09.000Z","msg":"根本就無後悔同反省過 人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f03c0f4e059ff7cc9c6dc24fe6375382a77bf9","tid":2516101,"uid":205765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"兩個仆街毫無悔意"},{"pid":"cb9a53b41fed08aff1fc9ba3a9c602e5e2c1dba6","tid":2516101,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:45:30.000Z","msg":"二條垃圾"},{"pid":"6eed8d17c9d5fc19604999d48acdd69042235677","tid":2516101,"uid":105891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6bc316b87c3523a7b972b7b7ca6ff6d5470ec21b","tid":2516101,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:15:03.000Z",